{"tid":2068312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要打擊濫捕，信我呢個方法","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:22:53.000Z","uid":99805,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"28e97f4f6017019b8e2cf2fe279537b4dbae5b6c","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"第一點就係網羅所有因運動告唔入既荒謬案件，列晒指證港警濫捕，講大話既案件，以證明唔係單一事件，並證明港警多次講大話並不可靠<br />\n<br />\n下一步要否決警察唔一定係誠實證人又好，打國際線又好，最緊要有條數據<br />\n係，我係好似精人出口，想搵笨人出手，無奈我無能力長期對住電腦，懇請求巴絲出手做research 比我搵一次笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，搵出荒謬既案例做對比，例如社工只係要求警方給予更多時間人群散去，卻換來監禁，持械傷人藍屍判三個月，更有法官贊傷人者高尚情操，法官包致金侄女影住佢兜巴打狗都只係判感化，又或者因為多名警察口供前後不對，反被指可信，疑點利益歸於被告既普通法已死<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地，唔做都幫手推下post<br />\n我今日開左第二次，好希望有巴絲幫手製作<br />\n先係清單又好，做個資料庫又好<br />\n所有濫捕，司法失衡既證據就由此起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e312cde3bd2d8778a80806cde55f4cb5c01617","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"推上去呀唔該"},{"pid":"2819c7b97724376d31b18376669949aa81b54e3a","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"柒婆條國安法宣傳片話搵到好多炸彈，證明一早埋下劇本用黎立國安，我地可以其人之道，搵出所有濫捕，司法制度被破壞既案例打擊對方"},{"pid":"a746a289f47ec73bae61ba81f034cc416d2e78a3","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"求你地幫下我<br />\n幫下香港"},{"pid":"e040aac83422c3e01b621dcc9e36895ac55216e1","tid":2068312,"uid":230196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a8bfe5a60dfff9e489e2fac7d97ba5e7d1a3ad","tid":2068312,"uid":178108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3aa6fd6f8a0e8f6ff3de96ad2860022f1be0a0bc","tid":2068312,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a198d61e879f49c9fcb4b242489a5a37f122314","tid":2068312,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"第一點可以包埋啲狗平時處理非手足案件，反正做嘢咁馬虎求其，一定都好多唔合理地方"},{"pid":"1c2c8d6f06f25aea3e592a7676f14ee934524b70","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:59:46.000Z","msg":"求下大家推上熱門"},{"pid":"a9099ae1acdc73bc5dc49e260b188d97a1c112f1","tid":2068312,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"呢到有班狗既濫權實錄 唔知有冇用<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=a20be68d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a>"},{"pid":"a62b0855bd73fd1e0f6054a382618c066564facb","tid":2068312,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"b2d450caa99414595cc620307a394eb97cb5d938","tid":2068312,"uid":83912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"推，同埋要搜集埋不公平判決既案例<br />\n感覺外國唔知手足乜都冇做就判暴動判各種罪"},{"pid":"d3c5b5027e706c750a9e6e3f10ba083fc1de4198","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"第二，搵出荒謬既案例做對比，例如社工只係要求警方給予更多時間人群散去，卻換來監禁<span style=\"color: red;\">一年</span>，持械傷人藍屍判三個月，更有法官贊傷人者高尚情操"},{"pid":"92f0d470e4cf833c19afa4e6d29bc4b3f2ca109f","tid":2068312,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"有point"},{"pid":"7ead3511459b6009d63d1b84438f85b642b8e200","tid":2068312,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83a9956063a8ef6c2bcce3375eeda25f950977d8","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9099ae1acdc73bc5dc49e260b188d97a1c112f1","tid":2068312,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"呢到有班狗既濫權實錄 唔知有冇用<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=a20be68d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"濫權唔夠力<br />\n最好係法庭判左既案<br />\n因為法座判左，個說服力大好多"},{"pid":"e88f9f67b6e9634ffe12011efa5fec66bc8e4476","tid":2068312,"uid":44874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9c1d16ccb00c9e9a5d9115f7b1ece5a82cc8e5","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83a9956063a8ef6c2bcce3375eeda25f950977d8","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9099ae1acdc73bc5dc49e260b188d97a1c112f1","tid":2068312,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"呢到有班狗既濫權實錄 唔知有冇用<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=a20be68d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"濫權唔夠力<br />\n最好係法庭判左既案<br />\n因為法座判左，個說服力大好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9e3ad719f820b9c96110c1136fd9a03e84fccf","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"推上去唔該"},{"pid":"ab30d93a7e8b7bd1fab2c30d202eb2dffc0d8755","tid":2068312,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"